high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the side table.
Take the pepper shaker from the table.
Turn around move towards floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take the pepper shaker from the table and Switch on the floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight, turn right towards the side table
Pick up pepper shaker from the side table
Turn around and go straight, turn left towards the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a pepper shaker by the light of a floor lamp

high_descs: Turn around and walk to a sidetable.
Pick up a pepper shaker from the sidetable.
Turn around, approach a floorlamp in the upper left corner, and lean upwards.
anns.task_desc: With the pepper shaker in hand, switch on the floorlamp.
